  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine the shredded red cabbage and julienne carrots.",
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the Kenyan sherry vinegar, olive oil, honey, bonito flakes, salt, and black pepper, and blend until smooth.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice and water to make a dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the cabbage mixture and toss to combine.",
    "Add the peppery cress leaves to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Season with additional salt and black pepper if needed.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cress leaves if desired."
